
API Key:

1, both versions need to replace YOUR_OPENWEATHERMAP_API_KEY with your actual OpenWeatherMap API key

Registered address: https://openweathermap.org/api

2. Permission Settings:

Android (React Native & Flutter):

The android/app/SRC/main/AndroidManifest. XML to add:
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION" />
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION" />
iOS (React Native & Flutter):
In ios/Runner/Info.plist add:
<key>NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
<string>We need your location to show local weather</string>
<key>NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
<string>We need your location to show local weather</string>
